    <div id="first" class="pointer">
      <div id="aboutus-head"><h2>About Weather Wise</h2></div>
      <div id="aboutus-body"><p>At Weather Wise, we are dedicated to delivering accurate and real-time weather information with an exceptional user experience. Born out of a shared passion for technology and innovation, we believe that weather data should not only be informative but also easy to access and visually appealing. Our mission is to make weather forecasting simple and reliable, helping users plan their day or stay informed about the latest weather conditions with ease.</p></div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="second" class="pointer">
      <div id="ourstory-head"><h2>Our Story</h2></div>
      <div id="ourstory-body"><p>The idea for Weather Wise was born among three friends, all students at NMIMS University, who shared a deep interest in technology and coding. Krutarth Patel, Om Anoakar, and Parshva Samdadiya were united by their curiosity for innovation and their desire to create something impactful. Inspired by the often-overlooked potential of weather apps, the trio embarked on a mission to redefine the way people interact with weather data.</p></div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="third" class="pointer">
      <div id="ourfounder-head"><h2>Our Founders</h2></div>
      <div id="ourfounder-body">
        <ul>
          <li><b>Krutarth Patel</b> - A visionary coder and project lead, Krutarth drives the technical development of Weather Wise. He oversees the app's architecture and ensures that it runs smoothly across all platforms.</li>
          <li><b>Om Anaokar</b> - Our database expert, Om handles the critical task of managing and optimizing Weather Wise's data infrastructure. His expertise ensures that the app delivers accurate and up-to-date weather information in real time.</li>
          <li><b>Parshva Samdadiya</b> - A designer with a keen eye for detail, Parshva ensures that Weather Wise offers an exceptional user experience. From the app's UI/UX to maintaining its logos and branding, Parshva makes sure that the design is modern, intuitive, and user-friendly.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="fourth" class="pointer">
